{"tid":589933,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"【食物解碼】生蠔裙邊愈黑代表愈污糟？　5大重點看生蠔是否新鮮","createTime":"2018-03-12T07:49:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-13T07:50:30.000Z","uid":10958,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"6e2ad83ba1f20823349599d05ef74a8c89f581a8","tid":589933,"uid":10958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T07:49:26.000Z","msg":"<strong>【食物解碼】生蠔裙邊愈黑代表愈污糟？　5大重點看生蠔是否新鮮</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/article/156956/thumbnail/7199fcb7301cc345f59253ce3564c83e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Farticle%2F156956%2Fthumbnail%2F7199fcb7301cc345f59253ce3564c83e.jpg&h=0057e132&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">生蠔深受港人歡迎，因此不少餐廳、酒店的自助餐都以即開生蠔作招徠，讓客人覺得「物有所值」！生蠔中除了蠔肉，還有帶黑色的裙帶，可是裙帶的顏色和新鮮度有關係嗎？裙邊愈黑代表愈髒？</span><br />\n<br />\n生蠔生長在鹹淡水交界或海水中，是濾食性的海產，牠們以水中的浮游生物為糧食，因此養殖水域的水質必需乾淨。生蠔的味道會因為水域、微生物種類和生長時間而受到影響，生蠔的裙邊呈啡黑色是正常的現象，那正正是因為海藻把裙邊染色的關係，所以裙邊的顏色深淺，關係到生長環境，並不代表生蠔骯髒。<br />\n<br />\n一般來說，生蠔以冬季出產的較為肥美，因夏天是生蠔的生殖期，肉質沒那麼飽滿。吃生蠔最重要的是新鮮與否，開殼後以新鮮食用為佳，否則蠔肉接觸到空氣，便容易滋生細菌，那麼我們挑選和購買時有什麼地方要注意呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1185007/xlarge/478dfd8b130bfef0b6ff83b15b9973b3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1185007%2Fxlarge%2F478dfd8b130bfef0b6ff83b15b9973b3.jpg&h=15e09c3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">1. 聞起來生蠔沒有異味。（視覺中國）</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1185011/xlarge/4c9e03dfd7dfb6b5ed011de68f63d200.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1185011%2Fxlarge%2F4c9e03dfd7dfb6b5ed011de68f63d200.jpg&h=1c053913&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">2. 生蠔的蠔殼緊閉，完整無損。（視覺中國）</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1185008/xlarge/2074a32b1f8cc63b866548a85dabcb30.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1185008%2Fxlarge%2F2074a32b1f8cc63b866548a85dabcb30.jpg&h=05f4ed02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">3. 蠔肉飽滿有光澤。（視覺中國）</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1185009/xlarge/f3e3a870d1d27970557a5edb6d49f7f9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1185009%2Fxlarge%2Ff3e3a870d1d27970557a5edb6d49f7f9.jpg&h=723a67a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">4.生蠔中帶海水。（視覺中國）</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1185010/xlarge/0da1596847aee62f1af97c006bee39fb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1185010%2Fxlarge%2F0da1596847aee62f1af97c006bee39fb.jpg&h=4685abcd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">5. 生蠔新鮮的話，刺激裙邊時，裙邊會動。（視覺中國）</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1185012/xlarge/71b530f2314d83f1547baa60d430414f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1185012%2Fxlarge%2F71b530f2314d83f1547baa60d430414f.jpg&h=01aa2fe9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">生蠔通常配搭白酒，帶出生蠔的鮮味。（視覺中國）</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1185013/xlarge/d45fa6ca14fdc5d993d998e1d3f2c54e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1185013%2Fxlarge%2Fd45fa6ca14fdc5d993d998e1d3f2c54e.jpg&h=98f18686&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">食用時可用叉子將蠔肉與蠔殼分離。（視覺中國）</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1185003/xlarge/9b71153bc5ef04d5b5648b9a9fae4479.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1185003%2Fxlarge%2F9b71153bc5ef04d5b5648b9a9fae4479.jpg&h=2508ad69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">開蠔的步驟示範。（視覺中國）</span><br />\n<br />\n很多人都說法國生蠔要在「R月份」品嘗，「R月份」是指9月至4月，英文中有R的月份。不過現時很多生蠔都是養殖的，因此一年四季都能吃到來自世界各地的生蠔。<br />\n<br />\n但是香港食物安全中心提醒，進食生蠔時要特別留意食物安全，因為生蠔本質上比其他海產危險，牠用過濾的方式進食，萬一生長環境附近有病毒和細菌，便容易在蠔內積聚。所以香港食物安全中心強調，進食生蠔或半生不熟的蠔，較易受到病原體感染，建議蠔類應徹底煮熟才食用。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/01%E6%95%99%E7%85%AE/156956/-%E9%A3%9F%E7%89%A9%E8%A7%A3%E7%A2%BC-%E7%94%9F%E8%A0%94%E8%A3%99%E9%82%8A%E6%84%88%E9%BB%91%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E6%84%88%E6%B1%A1%E7%B3%9F-5%E5%A4%A7%E9%87%8D%E9%BB%9E%E7%9C%8B%E7%94%9F%E8%A0%94%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E6%96%B0%E9%AE%AE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F01%25E6%2595%2599%25E7%2585%25AE%2F156956%2F-%25E9%25A3%259F%25E7%2589%25A9%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E7%25A2%25BC-%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%25A0%2594%25E8%25A3%2599%25E9%2582%258A%25E6%2584%2588%25E9%25BB%2591%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E6%2584%2588%25E6%25B1%25A1%25E7%25B3%259F-5%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2587%258D%25E9%25BB%259E%25E7%259C%258B%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%25A0%2594%25E6%2598%25AF%25E5%2590%25A6%25E6%2596%25B0%25E9%25AE%25AE&d=JpxaRj1s82kYk0V6mTQ66wdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=a81f7cb7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/01%E6%95%99%E7%85%AE/156956/-%E9%A3%9F%E7%89%A9%E8%A7%A3%E7%A2%BC-%E7%94%9F%E8%A0%94%E8%A3%99%E9%82%8A%E6%84%88%E9%BB%91%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E6%84%88%E6%B1%A1%E7%B3%9F-5%E5%A4%A7%E9%87%8D%E9%BB%9E%E7%9C%8B%E7%94%9F%E8%A0%94%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E6%96%B0%E9%AE%AE</a>"},{"pid":"e4d304a8dda158bc16576a9548e91ffea25dad5d","tid":589933,"uid":15394,"like":32,"dislike":5,"score":27,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T07:51:14.000Z","msg":"是撚但啦.....窮撚有撚機會食咩.......就算有人請，都咪撚食呀............食完腸胃炎放幾日病假 冇錢開飯呀..........................."},{"pid":"4ebc40fb4b19a43bac8212f72f4d0bcdee754d1e","tid":589933,"uid":5159,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4d304a8dda158bc16576a9548e91ffea25dad5d","tid":589933,"uid":15394,"like":32,"dislike":5,"score":27,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T07:51:14.000Z","msg":"是撚但啦.....窮撚有撚機會食咩.......就算有人請，都咪撚食呀...